@DataVisualizerApi_HostAddress = https://localhost:5213

### Register a new user
POST {{DataVisualizerApi_HostAddress}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "YourSecurePassword123"
}

